translated: Henri Julien Rousseau said the customs Rousseau (born in 1844 in Laval, died in 1910 in Paris) was a French painter, ranked among the naive painters.
original: Henri Julien Rousseau dit le douanier Rousseau (né en 1844 à Laval, mort en 1910 à Paris) est un peintre français, classé parmi les peintres naïfs.
